Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:53.52,EDCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HEB8574&\4c&H933D2D&\t(3820,4350,\3c&HA30E60&\4c&HF47FA7&)}如果温暖终将消失 我宁愿将之舍弃
